    public class MetaAnnotationBindingRegistry
extends CompletableBindingRegistry
    The MetaAnnotationBindingRegistry is a registry that tries to complete its list of bindings when an unknown one is detected. It uses the given ResourceStore to parse the annotation's type and find if it's annotated with @Stereotype,
